title: 3 Questions to Reprogram Yourself
itunes:title: 3 Questions to Reprogram Yourself
description:
From 0-7 years old we are programmed by what we are taught and what we see. The problem with that is that sometimes we are carrying around beliefs that are not ours. In this episode, I will teach you how to reprogram yourself in real time with 3 important questions.
